{"tid":798884,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇高手可以入嚟解釋下呢個現象 (多圖)","createTime":"2018-08-29T15:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T16:35:34.000Z","uid":110375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7553cc9d512c20440b4cd14372a17921d0f4d764","tid":798884,"uid":110375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/231520_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F231520_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7739f8a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻點解會圍住啲食物轉轉轉轉<br />\n<br />\n佢哋唔係應該拎完啲食物就搬返屋企?<br />\n<br />\n有時啲嘢食唔小心跌咗落地下隔咗一日都會見到呢個情況<br />\n<br />\n我睇啲留言有人話係因為 做指揮嘅嗰隻螞蟻死左 所以佢哋唔知去邊好就圍住轉"},{"pid":"d1f6a47c3277181ecc7a5267901c889a09de8cea","tid":798884,"uid":158585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:43:55.000Z","msg":"唔想比其他人入去搶野食囉"},{"pid":"c8a583fb9b39648ff44077e0e223b5faff29c8bb","tid":798884,"uid":130568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"螞蟻死亡漩渦 (Ant mill)<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%9E%9E%E8%9F%BB%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%BC%A9%E6%B8%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%259E%259E%25E8%259F%25BB%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E6%25BC%25A9%25E6%25B8%25A6&d=ZLa2RPOie54rL0mnB2p4wwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=255ec50d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%9E%9E%E8%9F%BB%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E6%BC%A9%E6%B8%A6</a>"},{"pid":"fb6d0ed829232e4dcfd2ba73d62f7c2621772b9a","tid":798884,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ant_mill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAnt_mill&d=ZLa2RPOie54rL0mnB2p4wwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a70